{"tid":1277010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7月2 登記做選民！！！最後限期","createTime":"2019-07-02T05:45:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T15:12:02.000Z","uid":89538,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a8466d788084088494a4021ed755180a782a011c","tid":1277010,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:45:12.000Z","msg":"登記呀dllm！<br />\n網上仲黎得切<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voterregistration.gov.hk/chi/home.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voterregistration.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fhome.htm&d=Mrz8gheyF4cbCiJyPb%2FME3psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=47f66241\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voterregistration.gov.hk/chi/home.htm</a><br />\n<br />\nFyi<br />\n問九 : 我在2019年9月底才滿十八歲，而 2019年的選民新登記限期則是 7月 2日，我現在可不可以先登記做選民？<br />\n答九 : 2019年正式選民登記冊將在2019年9月25日或之前發表。若你在該日期或之前年滿十八歲，又是香港永久性居民，就符合資格，現在已可以申請登記做選民。"},{"pid":"72bc046cf0aaac5eb06b2782e5935e0af0449a9d","tid":1277010,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:48:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d578381c35d4528793b2c4f01041b32e5096364f","tid":1277010,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:48:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4c46c1a89f4a67ff5027043ebedc89eb817cf164","tid":1277010,"uid":62373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:48:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec0f49ea8fbf0ebf5554c14385c3a6dce287ac51","tid":1277010,"uid":270859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:48:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"943c36e33e8f2d8b4916bc9a6202829fd25da8c2","tid":1277010,"uid":267953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:48:55.000Z","msg":"快啲登記啊！！！！"},{"pid":"09bfc5dad9c95a7702a05da89d90e986ad43a73b","tid":1277010,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi